MCRT is a web application built on top of .Net framework using Asp.Net MVC (MVC 5) as an architectural pattern. The user interface of the application is built using Html 5, CSS3, Jquery / Javascript client libraries (typescript). For data storage and data querying , SQL Server (2012) is used as RDBMS. It also uses MS Power BI for data visualization and reporting. MCRT is hosted on windows platform (local domain machine) with IIS express and .NET Framework, supporting windows authentication. Application authorizes and manages its users and their roles using its own user access management interface. 
